  <title class="- topic/title ">Show or Hide Campaign Details</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">You can choose whether to show campaign
	 details. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
    <context id="context_2E80025F169240F099A0386646233335" class="- topic/section task/context ">
      <p class="- topic/p ">
        <ul id="ul_8BC4FB857C9B44FDB50DA7FB84BC8AE8" class="- topic/ul ">
          <li id="li_8A26D4AD55194E4D9961137A397528E0" class="- topic/li "> To
			 show the campaign type, targeting information, the campaign's start and end
			 dates, and the campaign priority, click 
			 <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Show campaign
				details</uicontrol>. 
		  </li>
          <li id="li_BE052734D37948E3AC685C59D630127A" class="- topic/li "> If
			 the details are already showing, you can hide them by clicking 
			 <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Hide campaign
				details</uicontrol>. 
		  </li>
        </ul>
      </p>
    </context>
